    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "Alamogordo, N.M. - At least 29 White Sands Missile",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "Range personnel were eyewitnesses to one or more",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "Unidentified Flying Objects between 10.30 and 11",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "a.m. Thursday.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "News concerning the UFOs has been cutoff by",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "orders from the Pentagon.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "All service personnel and civilians working for the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "services have been forbidden to discuss the sight-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "ings.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "An investigation is under way at Holloman Air",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "Force Base, N.M., with Maj. James Stephens, UFO",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "officer, in charge. He, too, is not allowed to discuss",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "the sightings.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "Terry Clark, president and general manager of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "radio station KALG, Alamogordo, said the UFOs first",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "were spotted near Ruidoso, N.M., then went near",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "Holloman AFB, then south toward Orogrande, N.M.,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "and then disappeared over the Sacramento Moun-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "tains.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "Information officers at Holloman AFB and WSMR",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "were contacted by Clark and he was told the Flight",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "Safety Office at Kirtland AFB at Albuquerque, N.M.,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "would handle the investigation. Kirtland would make",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "no comment except that all information would have to",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "come from the Pentagon.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "Clark called the assigned number at the Pentagon",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "and was told that no information was available.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "Capt. Frank J. Morris, director of information at",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "Holloman AFB, Saturday night said that Maj. Step-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "hens is handling the investigation. He said the re-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "ports would be sent to Wright-Patterson AFB, Ohio,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "and from there would go to the Pentagon. He said",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "text": "no information would be released except through the",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 53,
